'''亞倫·溫莎·萊維'''（[[英文|英文]]: Aaron Winsor  Levie，發音/ærənlɛvi/<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?video=3000086538&play=1 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013145/http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?video=3000086538&play=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一位[[美國|美國]][[企業家|企業家]]。他是[[Box公司|Box公司]]創辦人與[[執行長|執行長]]<ref name="SeattleTimesInvest"/> ，於2012年時超過11,000,000人以及120,000企業人士於世界各地使用者<ref name="LATIMES">{{cite web | last=Maltais | first=Michelle | title=Out of the Box with CEO Aaron Levie | publisher=LA Times | date=8 May 2012 | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/may/08/business/la-fi-tn-box-aaron-levie-20120507 | accessdate=23 August 2012 | archive-date=2017-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030053030/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/may/08/business/la-fi-tn-box-aaron-levie-20120507 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Box raises $125M for aggressive growth around the globe|url=http://venturebeat.com/2012/07/31/box-125m-funding/|accessdate=2014-04-08|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805193250/https://venturebeat.com/2012/07/31/box-125m-funding/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的淨資產估計為1億美元。

==教育與生活背景==
亞倫·萊維出生在[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]][[西雅圖|西雅圖]]於1985年<ref name=mercury>{{cite news|last=Cassidy|first=Mike|title=Cassidy: Silicon Valley start-ups provide their own education|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_17414725|accessdate=19 February 2014|newspaper=San Jose Mercury News|date=17 February 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090524/http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_17414725|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。從小在[[默瑟島|默瑟島]]成長並於[[默瑟島高中|默瑟島高中]]畢業。萊維也曾就讀於[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]，並同時於2005年休學，也開始從事[[Box公司|Box雲端儲存公司]]<ref name=mercury /><ref name="entrepreneur">{{cite web |last=Holland |first=Joel |url=http://www.entrepreneur.com/article/207510 |title=I'm an Entrepreneur; Get Me Out of Here! |publisher=Entrepreneur.com |date=2010-07-16 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919050005/https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/207510 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
這個想法的起源作為萊維正致力[[Box公司|Box]]於2004年一所大學的商務計劃。該計劃研究，為商業的雲端儲存選擇和聯繫幾個組織且詢問外界人士是如何儲存他們的內容和數據後，萊維來到該市場得到了是零散的結論。萊維發現了機會並建立一個線上的檔案儲存的服務，以此針對個人訪問並儲存文件和檔案<ref name=mercury />。

2005年12月，在此期間也是他在南加州大學三年級，萊維休學後並與他的朋友和Box的首席財務官開啟了[[Box公司|Box]]（原名[[Box公司|box.net]]） ，[[迪倫·史密斯|迪倫·史密斯]]就讀[[杜克大學|杜克大學]]。當時，[[Box公司|Box]]裡的儲存服務，用戶可以透過雲端來儲存他們的檔案<ref name=mercury />。

2005年4月，萊維和史密斯結合了[[Box公司|Box]]，而共同所經營公司搬出史密斯的家長在[[默瑟島|默瑟島]]的房子。不久後，他們公司搬到了[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[伯克利市|伯克利市]]。萊維和史密斯之首次擁有擔保的Box天使投資來自[[得克薩斯州|得克薩斯州]]億萬富翁[[馬克·庫班|馬克·庫班]]的電子郵件<ref name="SeattleTimesInvest"/><ref name="huffingtonpost">{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/billrobinson/aaron-levie-and-box-think_b_1190067.html |title=Bill Robinson: Aaron Levie and Box: Thinking Outside Of It |publisher=Huffingtonpost.com |date=2012-01-10 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2017-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901184719/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/billrobinson/aaron-levie-and-box-think_b_1190067.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Matt Rosoff |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/boxnet-just-scored-81-million-heres-what-theyll-spend-it-on-2011-10 |title=Box.net Just Scored $81 Million - Here's What They'll Spend It On |publisher=Business Insider |date=2011-10-11 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016133719/https://www.businessinsider.com/boxnet-just-scored-81-million-heres-what-theyll-spend-it-on-2011-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年，作為消費者的雲端儲存市場變得越來越壅塞，於是萊維和史密斯決定從消費者服務轉向一個專注於銷售的[[Box公司|Box公司]]（雲端儲存）。

於2012年，[[Box公司|Box]]將服務拓展到[[歐洲|歐洲]]，其第一家分公司在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]開幕<ref name="TechRadarEurope">{{cite news| last Austin =| first =Marcus| coauthors =| title =US Cloud Storage Player Box Come To The UK| newspaper =Tech Radar| location =| pages =| language =| publisher =| date =21 June 2012| url =http://www.techradar.com/us/news/world-of-tech/roundup/us-cloud-storage-player-box-comes-to-the-uk-1086522| accessdate =20 December 2012| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20131102162043/http://www.techradar.com/us/news/world-of-tech/roundup/us-cloud-storage-player-box-comes-to-the-uk-1086522| archive-date =2013-11-02| dead-url =yes}}</ref> 。 截至2014年，Box報導，世界500強企業有40 ％都支付於Box客戶<ref name="The New York Times">{{cite news| last Austin =| first =Hardy, Quentin (24 March 2014)| coauthors =| title =Box, a Cloud Storage Firm, Plans I.P.O.| newspaper =The New York Times| location =| pages =| language =| publisher =| date =26 March 2014| url =http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/25/technology/box-a-cloud-storage-firm-plans-ipo.html| accessdate =2014-04-08| archive-date =2014-04-07| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140407172922/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/25/technology/box-a-cloud-storage-firm-plans-ipo.html| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

===口語與寫作貢獻===
萊維曾在產界的事件，如財富頭腦風暴技術，Dreamforce，LeWeb，RSA，MobileBeat，GigaOm結構，TechCrunch破壞與DEMO。他還撰寫了關於如何創新之文章在科技行業出版物，如[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]，[[CNN.com|CNN.com]]，財富，[[福布斯|福布斯]]與快速公司<ref name="bare_url_a">{{cite web |url=http://allthingsd.com/20120306/a-visit-with-box-nets-aaron-levie-at-his-new-office-video/ |title=A Visit With Box.net's Aaron Levie at His New Office (Video) - Arik Hesseldahl - Enterprise |publisher=AllThingsD |date=2012-03-06 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410221556/http://allthingsd.com/20120306/a-visit-with-box-nets-aaron-levie-at-his-new-office-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://thisweekin.com/thisweekin-startups/aaron-levie-of-box-on-this-week-in-startups-224/ |title=Aaron Levie of Box on This Week in Startups #224 | ThisWeekIn |publisher=Thisweekin.com |date= |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413121530/http://thisweekin.com/thisweekin-startups/aaron-levie-of-box-on-this-week-in-startups-224/ |archive-date=2012-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Aaron Levie |url=http://vator.tv/news/2011-12-02-aaron-levie-on-boxnets-competitive-edge |title=VatorNews - Aaron Levie on Box's competitive edge |publisher=Vator.tv |date=2011-12-02 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016133204/https://vator.tv/news/2011-12-02-aaron-levie-on-boxnets-competitive-edge |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Kym McNicholas |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/kymmcnicholas/2011/08/05/why-box-nets-ceo-aaron-levies-the-next-david-copperfield/ |title=Why Box.net's CEO Aaron Levie's The Next David Copperfield |publisher=Forbes |date=2011-05-08 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016133156/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kymmcnicholas/2011/08/05/why-box-nets-ceo-aaron-levies-the-next-david-copperfield/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==獎項與表彰==
2012年，萊維被評為具快速公司產生流量領導之一。快速公司也把他自己的大部分業務列表創新人才於2011年。萊維於企業雜誌前30名企業家之一<ref name="30MostCEO">{{cite web | last= | first= | title=30 Most Influential Under 30 CEOs of 2010 | publisher=Under 30 CEO | date=11 January 2011 | url=http://under30ceo.com/30-most-influential-under30ceos-of-2010/ | accessdate=23 August 2012 | archive-date=2020-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127061711/https://www.under30ceo.com/30-most-influential-under30ceos-of-2010/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="inc">{{cite web |url=http://www.inc.com/30under30/2008/profile/89-leviesmith.html |title=Top 30 Entrepreneurs Under 30 - Aaron Levie and Dylan Smith, Box.net |publisher=Inc.com |year=2008 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-date=2012-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609063739/http://www.inc.com/30under30/2008/profile/89-leviesmith.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他還獲得榮譽來自[[矽谷|矽谷]][[聖何塞|聖何塞]]商業雜誌（40與40歲以下）與[[邱吉爾俱樂部|邱吉爾俱樂部]]<ref name="SanJoseBizJournal">{{cite news | last = | first = | coauthors = | title =40 Under 40: Aaron Levie | newspaper =San Jose Biz Journal | location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date =1 December 2011 | url =http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/news/2011/11/29/40-under-40-aaron-levie.html | accessdate =20 December 2012 | archive-date =2014-03-27 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140327015748/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/news/2011/11/29/40-under-40-aaron-levie.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。在萊維的領導下，Box本身已獲得無數個行業獎項，在2011年和2012年被列入為[[德勤科技|德勤科技]]之高成長500強名單內。Box在2010年和2011年中為[[舊金山|舊金山]]商業雜誌上被評為成長最快之私人公司的一個。

